verbose_text: Cold exposure increased IL-6 expression in both chow fed (p < 0.001, XREF_FIG J) and HFD fed (p < 0.0001, XREF_FIG K) mice; however, the relative expression levels of IL-6 in HFD fed cold exposed mice were lower (p < 0.05, XREF_FIG L) when compared to those in chow fed cold exposed mice.
